                    <div id="dnn_ctr15884_ModuleContent" class="DNNModuleContent ModDNNHTMLC">
                        <div id="dnn_ctr15884_HtmlModule_lblContent">
                            <h2 style="text-align: left;">Study English in a global city or on a world-class university campus</h2>
                            <p> Prepare for study, work and life in an English-speaking country with one of INTO’s English language courses. The courses run throughout the year, and you will be taught by experienced and supportive tutors.</p>
                            <p>From scenic towns to vibrant cities, INTO can help you improve your English in a world-class university location in either the <a href="/en/study-abroad/country-guides/uk" title="UK destination guide">UK</a> or <a href="/en/campaigns/us/study-in-the-us" title="US destination guide">US</a>. You’ll practise your new skills with native English speakers, make new friends from all over the world, and experience the local culture in every way possible. And of course, INTO will support you every step of the way.</p>
                            <h3>Is an INTO English language course right for me?</h3>
                            <p> INTO English language courses are designed for you if you are an international student and you:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li>don’t meet the English language requirements for further academic study</li>
                                <li>would like to improve your communication skills to make the most of your studies</li>
                                <li>want to be immersed in the English language and practise with local English-speaking people</li>
                                <li>would like to enjoy a sociable, memorable and fulfilling experience</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>Whatever your requirements or current abilities, INTO has a course for you!</p>
                            <h3>Which English language course do I need?</h3>
                            <p>To find out more about the courses on offer at our Centres in the UK and US, see below.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- End_Module_15884 -->
                </div>
